arStrings.szText: "The people of Nahantu know me as their champion. What else do I need to do?"
Well done. Your deeds are known far and wide in Nahantu. But now Ormus must ask you to find one of his most trusted councilors, Sihek, who has gone missing in the Kurast Undercity.
Venture below, locate Sihek, and assist him with his mission.
